comments: Love (MIA) establishes himself in Burks' (DET) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Hayes (DET) exits the paint within three seconds.
Adebayo (MIA) establishes himself in Cunningham's (DET) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Stewart (DET) extends his off arm into Butler's (MIA) back, and dislodges Butler from his rebounding position. Affecting his ability to  pursue the loose ball.
Lowry (MIA) initiates contact with Burks (DET) that affects his FOM off-ball.
Adebayo (MIA) is moving alongside Cunningham's (DET) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together during the drive.
As Butler (MIA) gains possession of the ball, he legally keeps the ball in play by releasing it to his teammate before his foot steps out of bounds.
Burks (DET) swipes down and initiates contact with Herro's (MIA) arm, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Adebayo (MIA) is last to make contact with the ball before it goes out of bounds. DET is correctly rewarded possession.
Lowry (MIA) initiates contact with Burks' (DET) right arm, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Herro (MIA) just gets the ball established into the front court within 8 seconds.
Stewart (DET) fails to fully clear the lane and is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Hayes (DET) legally contests Love's (MIA) jump shot, making "high-five" contact to Love's off hand after the ball is released.
Adebayo (MIA) reaches out for the loose ball and incidental hand-on-ball contact with Duren (DET) occurs.
